    "features": [
      "Pair Sold: Each package includes 2 panels of black blackout curtains. Each panel measures 40\"W x 84\"L, with a pair measuring 80\"W x 84\"L. The black thermal insulated curtains have 2 hanging options (Rod pocket & Clip Style) with a 3-inch rod pocket to fit 1.5-inch rods. Multiple colors and sizes are available to meet your preferences",
      "Room Darkening Curtains: WelvetBLK blackout curtains can block 80%-95% of light and UV rays, shading effectiveness increases as color darkness intensifies. Shield your room from strong midday sunlight to cut down on glare and create a warm, relaxing environment",
      "High-Quality Fabric: Crafted from premium polyester fiber and with a triple-layer blackout fabric, these curtains blend a soft texture with durability to expertly block light and ensure uncompromising privacy and noise-reducing properties, making them both functional and elegant for any space",
      "Energy Saving: Keeping rooms cool in summer by blocking sunlight and reducing AC use, and warm in winter by retaining heat, thus lowering energy costs. In multi - room settings, its uniform color on both sides allows for seamless coordination across living rooms, bedrooms, and offices, creating a consistent, elegant look while its light - blocking and privacy features suit various room functions",
      "Easy Care: WelvetBLK blackout curtains 84 inch length 2 panel is machine washable for easy care and maintenance. Use only non-chlorine bleach when needed, tumble dry low, and warm iron as needed"
